{"id": "figure_012", "modality": "figures", "name": "Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a Squeeze-and-Excitation (SE) block embedded in a residual block. Title 'Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block' at top in 32px bold. Main path bottom to top: input feature map 'X (H x W x C)' -> a 'Residual Conv Block (F_tr)' -> feature map 'U (H x W x C)'. From U, the SE branch splits to the RIGHT: '1) Squeeze: Global Average Pool -> 1 x 1 x C' -> '2) Excitation: FC -> ReLU -> FC -> Sigmoid (1 x 1 x C)' producing a per-channel scale vector 's'. Then '3) Scale: U \u2299 s (channel-wise multiply)' recombines the SE scale with U via a '\u2299' (element-wise multiply) node. Finally a residual skip-connection arrow carries X around the whole block to a '+' addition node producing the output. Annotate the reduction ratio 'r' in the excitation (C -> C/r -> C). The squeeze/excitation branch and the residual skip must be DISTINCT paths that do not cross through the main conv box. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All components (X input, Residual Conv Block, U, Squeeze GAP, Excitation FC-ReLU-FC-Sigmoid, Scale multiply \u2299, residual + node, output) are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "The Squeeze step is labelled as Global Average Pool producing a 1 x 1 x C descriptor", "The Excitation step shows the FC -> ReLU -> FC -> Sigmoid sequence with the reduction-ratio annotation (C -> C/r -> C)", "The Scale '\u2299' channel-wise-multiply node combines U with the excitation vector s", "The residual skip-connection arrow carries X around the whole block to a separate '+' addition node and does not pass through the conv box", "The SE branch path and the residual skip path are visually distinct and do not overlap each other", "Tensor-shape annotations (H x W x C, 1 x 1 x C) are legible and do not collide with other text", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 1, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5303, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5203}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5310, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 24005}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5837, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 13887}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_012_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_012_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n        <!-- Definitions for arrowheads and patterns -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" \n                    refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#34495e\" />\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" \n                    refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" />\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-blue\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" \n                    refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#3498db\" />\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n\n        <!-- Input Feature Map -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"800\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"825\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"845\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">X</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"860\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n\n        <!-- Main Conv Block -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"600\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Residual</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Conv Block</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"665\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">F_tr</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"685\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\u2192 H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n\n        <!-- Feature Map U -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"400\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Feature Map</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">U</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n\n        <!-- SE Branch: Squeeze -->\n        <rect x=\"350\" y=\"380\" width=\"140\" height=\"120\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">1) Squeeze</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Global Average</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Pool</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">\u2192 1\u00d71\u00d7C</text>\n\n        <!-- SE Branch: Excitation -->\n        <rect x=\"550\" y=\"350\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">2) Excitation</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">FC (C \u2192 C/r)</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ReLU</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">FC (C/r \u2192 C)</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"640\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Sigmoid</text>\n        <text x=\"680\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" font-weight=\"bold\">r = reduction</text>\n        <text x=\"680\" y=\"407\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" font-weight=\"bold\">ratio</text>\n\n        <!-- Scale Vector s -->\n        <rect x=\"800\" y=\"400\" width=\"100\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"850\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Scale Vector</text>\n        <text x=\"850\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">s</text>\n        <text x=\"850\" y=\"460\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">(1 \u00d7 1 \u00d7 C)</text>\n\n        <!-- Element-wise Multiply Node -->\n        <circle cx=\"950\" cy=\"300\" r=\"30\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"950\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">\u2299</text>\n\n        <!-- Scale Operation -->\n        <rect x=\"1050\" y=\"260\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1120\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">3) Scale</text>\n        <text x=\"1120\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">U \u2299 s</text>\n        <text x=\"1120\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n\n        <!-- Addition Node -->\n        <circle cx=\"1300\" cy=\"300\" r=\"30\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1300\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">+</text>\n\n        <!-- Output -->\n        <rect x=\"1400\" y=\"260\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1460\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Output</text>\n        <text x=\"1460\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Y</text>\n        <text x=\"1460\" y=\"320\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n\n        <!-- Main Path Arrows -->\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"800\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"730\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"490\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- SE Branch Arrows -->\n        <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"340\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"490\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"730\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"790\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Scale path -->\n        <line x1=\"850\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"850\" y2=\"330\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <line x1=\"850\" y1=\"330\" x2=\"920\" y2=\"330\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- U to multiply -->\n        <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"440\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"280\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"270\" x2=\"920\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- After multiply to scale -->\n        <line x1=\"980\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"1040\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Scale to addition -->\n        <line x1=\"1190\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"1270\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Skip connection -->\n        <line x1=\"100\" y1=\"840\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"840\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"840\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <line x1=\"50\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"1270\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Addition to output -->\n        <line x1=\"1330\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"1390\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Legend Box -->\n        <rect x=\"1550\" y=\"450\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" rx=\"8\" \n              fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1700\" y=\"480\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">LEGEND</text>\n        \n        <!-- Legend Items -->\n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"500\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"515\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Feature Maps</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"530\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#fff3cd\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"545\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Conv Operations</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"560\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#f8d7da\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"575\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">SE Operations</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"590\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#d1ecf1\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"605\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Scale Vector</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"620\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#d4edda\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"635\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Scaling</text>\n        \n        <circle cx=\"1585\" cy=\"660\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#6c757d\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"665\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Operations (\u2299, +)</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"690\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"690\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"695\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Main Path</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"710\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"710\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"715\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">SE Branch</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"730\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"730\" stroke=\"#17a2b8\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"735\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Scale Path</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"750\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"750\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"755\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Skip Connection</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"770\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"770\" stroke=\"#28a745\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"775\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Scaled Features</text>\n\n        <!-- Tensor Shape Annotations -->\n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"810\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"830\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">H = Height, W = Width</text>\n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"845\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">C = Channels, r = Reduction</text>\n\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Squeeze-and-Excitation Residual Block</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n        <!-- Main Flow Path -->\n        <!-- Input X -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"800\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"830\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Input X</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"850\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- Residual Conv Block -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"600\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"630\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Residual</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"650\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Conv Block</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"670\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(F_tr)</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#fadbd8\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- Feature Map U -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"400\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"430\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">U</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#e8daef\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- SE Branch -->\n        <!-- 1) Squeeze: Global Average Pool -->\n        <rect x=\"350\" y=\"380\" width=\"140\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">1) Squeeze:</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">Global Avg Pool</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"430\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#fdebd0\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d71\u00d71\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- Squeezed tensor -->\n        <rect x=\"550\" y=\"390\" width=\"100\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#f1c40f\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"410\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">1\u00d71\u00d7C</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#7d6608\" font-size=\"9\">B\u00d71\u00d71\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- 2) Excitation: FC layers -->\n        <rect x=\"720\" y=\"350\" width=\"160\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">2) Excitation:</text>\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">FC \u2192 ReLU \u2192 FC</text>\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">\u2192 Sigmoid</text>\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"9\">C \u2192 C/r \u2192 C</text>\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#d5f4e6\" font-size=\"9\">B\u00d71\u00d71\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- Reduction ratio annotation -->\n        <text x=\"800\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">r = reduction ratio</text>\n        \n        <!-- Scale vector s -->\n        <rect x=\"950\" y=\"390\" width=\"80\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#16a085\" stroke=\"#138d75\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n        <text x=\"990\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">s</text>\n        <text x=\"990\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"9\">(1\u00d71\u00d7C)</text>\n        \n        <!-- 3) Scale: Element-wise multiply -->\n        <circle cx=\"420\" cy=\"250\" r=\"30\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\">\u2299</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">3) Scale</text>\n        <text x=\"420\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"9\">U \u2299 s</text>\n        \n        <!-- Scaled feature map -->\n        <rect x=\"550\" y=\"210\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#8e44ad\" stroke=\"#7d3c98\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"610\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Scaled U</text>\n        <text x=\"610\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n        <text x=\"610\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#e8daef\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7H\u00d7W\u00d7C</text>\n        \n        <!-- Residual Addition -->\n        <circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"150\" r=\"25\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"158\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\">+</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">Residual Add</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output -->\n        <rect x=\"100\" y=\"50\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" stroke=\"#1b2631\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"75\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">Output</text>\n        <text x=\"160\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\">(H \u00d7 W \u00d7 C)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrows -->\n        <!-- Main path arrows -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-blue\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#3498db\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-orange\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e67e22\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n        \n        <!-- Main flow -->\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"800\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"730\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"600\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"490\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- SE branch -->\n        <line x1=\"220\" y1=\"440\" x2=\"340\" y2=\"410\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"490\" y1=\"410\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"410\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"650\" y1=\"410\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"400\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"880\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"410\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Scale operation -->\n        <line x1=\"990\" y1=\"390\" x2=\"450\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"400\" x2=\"390\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"450\" y1=\"250\" x2=\"540\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Residual connection -->\n        <path d=\"M 80 840 Q 50 840 50 400 Q 50 150 130 150\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Final output -->\n        <line x1=\"610\" y1=\"210\" x2=\"185\" y2=\"165\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <line x1=\"160\" y1=\"125\" x2=\"160\" y2=\"120\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <rect x=\"1200\" y=\"50\" width=\"650\" height=\"400\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"1525\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\">LEGEND</text>\n        \n        <!-- Legend items -->\n        <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"100\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"115\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Input/Output Tensors</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"130\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"145\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Convolutional Operations</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"160\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"175\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Squeeze Operations</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"190\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"205\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Excitation (FC + Activations)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1220\" y=\"220\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"235\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Feature Maps</text>\n        \n        <circle cx=\"1235\" cy=\"260\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#e67e22\" stroke=\"#d35400\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"265\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Element-wise Operations</text>\n        \n        <circle cx=\"1235\" cy=\"290\" r=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"295\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Addition Operations</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"1250\" y2=\"320\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"325\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Main Data Flow</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"350\" x2=\"1250\" y2=\"350\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"355\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">SE Branch Flow</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1220\" y1=\"380\" x2=\"1250\" y2=\"380\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\"/>\n        <text x=\"1260\" y=\"385\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">Residual Skip Connection</text>\n        \n        <text x=\"1220\" y=\"415\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n        <text x=\"1220\" y=\"430\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\">B = Batch size, H = Height, W = Width, C = Channels</text>\n        \n        <!-- Process Flow Labels -->\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"500\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\">SE Block Process:</text>\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"520\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">1. Squeeze: Global pooling reduces spatial dims</text>\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"540\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">2. Excitation: FC layers learn channel weights</text>\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"560\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">3. Scale: Apply weights to original features</text>\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"580\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\">4. Residual: Add skip connection for training</text>\n        \n        <!-- Component count annotation -->\n        <text x=\"1400\" y=\"620\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" font-size=\"10\">Total Components: 14 labeled elements</text>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>"}